<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>It depends on where you are.  If you're in an OOW or later expansion, not so good damage wise, hitting around maybe 120ish max, but still lots of HP usually.  If you charm in Vxed you can have a pet that hits for 1200.   <br /> <br />There really is not comparision between regular pets and charmed ones.  They're two totally separate animals, with pros and cons of each depending on which zone you may be in that you charm.</p>
