<p>in OOW+ reverse charming is better than charming. <br /> <br />Short version <br />Root Mob <br />Charm mob <br />Buff mob <br />Break Charm <br />Reroot mob <br />Slow mob <br />Charm mob <br />Send new unbuffed slowed mob against old hasted pet rerooting as needed <br />at about 5% back off pet. <br />Break charm <br />Nuke down now almost dead pet. <br />Repeat 4-5 times untill you finally have to kill the hasted one. and start completly over.</p>
