<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>When someone's referring to how hard a mob hits, they're referring to a single hit.  So a mob that hits for 2K that quads could conceivably do 8K of damage in a round.  (Squish!) <br /> <br />Most OoW mobs I've seen quad... so the charmed ones can do max about 600 per round, but more usually hit for about 250-300 per round. <br /> <br />And SBS... interesting tactic.  I'm going to have to go try that one out, though I can only wince at the results if for whatever reason root and charm both broke at the same time.  Where's a ranger to snare? ;D <br /></p>
